{"tid":1710232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呢兩日感覺到大師兄返嚟喇","createTime":"2019-11-12T06:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:10:11.000Z","uid":195248,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67c682106cdc4b239ae0ca47125ffdf36430f8d1","tid":1710232,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"大三罷之前運動已經明顯到樽頸位<br />\n呢兩日行動咁成功係因為前所有未既各區開花<br />\n回想返6月到8月<br />\n我地每個星期都有唔同手足搞新活動開發領域<br />\n<strong></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國歌</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場和你飛</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手拖手人鏈</span></span></strong><br />\n仲有好多好多<br />\n每一個活動都係百花齊放<br />\n而最重要既係<br />\n人係有貪新鮮感同厭倦感<br />\n自從10月1之後 運動就主要係裝修同開花<br />\n好多人都參與唔到同埋每次都做同一樣野<br />\n日後要keep到個勢 大家一定要諗到有效又創意無限既活動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2e2bcc44fb980532aa5419a36a0737ad17421383","tid":1710232,"uid":258598,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8666e609dab5924d5daaecec05b586eae39e74d5","tid":1710232,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">出門前入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n將今日警察炮轟校園推上國際<br />\n入 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/task</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=f66c8164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n有Telegram的人請加入<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Twitter共識Channel</span><br />\ntwitter組每日會更新主線副線任務<br />\n方便大家知道每日有咩議員外媒國際大事<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + 響原Tweet reply</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=UyoO8KdNfTPb55o7yEEco4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=5c751d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a>"},{"pid":"0289e29aa755a9b7e166d31ae836812a8a05aaff","tid":1710232,"uid":195248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e2bcc44fb980532aa5419a36a0737ad17421383","tid":1710232,"uid":258598,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"呢樣當然係其中一樣<br />\n但係唔可能每次都要手足付出生命嚟換取返對運動熱情<br />\n要代佢地行埋落去就要搵到突破點"},{"pid":"efeaa859fe73eb7e03eeb08a4629b5e4088d7b01","tid":1710232,"uid":55144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9df18c013b491c7e23054c559a39159ffa2fe87","tid":1710232,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}